      label(for="password" style="margin-left:15px") Password 
      span(style="font-size:.6rem;margin-left:15px;margin-top:-10px") âŒž Basically zero requirements for password here, just don't leave empty
      input#password(type="password" name="password"  required='true' placeholder='********')

    div.form-control 
      label(for="passConfirm" style="margin-left:15px") Confirm Password
      input#passConfirm(type="password" name="passConfirm"  required='true' placeholder='********')

